    ${enabled_user_count}=
    ...  Get Lines Containing String  ${resp}  Enabled User Count
    ${maximum_ids}=  Get Lines Containing String  ${resp}  Maximum IDs
    Should Contain  ${enabled_user_count}  2
    Should Contain  ${maximum_ids}  15


